在打的是「中共政權保衛戰」，而你們僅僅是在打「香港生活方式保衛戰」</strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"bae108fbd30916aa44a1e5b58dcd47d6293624ae","tid":1725921,"uid":85425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:14:10.000Z","msg":"藍黃是政見,黑白是良知,為伯伯搞頭7"},{"pid":"0976547af2b3254a2fb9445ecf029b760ca5bba4","tid":1725921,"uid":75982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"TUI"},{"pid":"819b96c1805b7c572078cfd9cdd761c71e034f80","tid":1725921,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:17:35.000Z","msg":"個搞手 要負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e948fd2d2840596ec12f18036c78e21a236df4","tid":1725921,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:17:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: 